Set Height 750
Source "recordings/tapes/shared-config.tape"
Output "recordings/svgs/tools/list-search-no-results.svg"
Output "recordings/ascii/tools/list-search-no-results.ascii"

Hide
Type "# List with no results"
Enter
Show
Type "composio tools list --toolkits 'nonexistent'"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 6s
